    "bio": `
    I'm a Software Engineer from Pakistan building full-stack web applications with the MERN stack — React.js, Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB/MySQL — with a focus on clean, scalable, production-ready code.

I currently work at KIPS Education System, where I build and maintain production websites and solve real-world technical problems at scale.

Right now, I'm building an Agentic RAG Chat Application — a chatbot that goes beyond simple Q&A, using LangChain to orchestrate multi-step reasoning and tool-calling over custom knowledge bases. It's built with Next.js and Node.js/TypeScript on the backend, Qdrant for vector search, and MySQL for structured data. The MVP is complete and working end-to-end.

My project work also spans e-commerce (Affiliate Marketing module at Decimal Solution), Android development with real-time database integration (NADRA), and a sentiment-analysis platform for smartphone reviews using Python and the DeBERTa model.

I'm committed to continuous learning and staying current with emerging web and AI technologies — and I actively use AI-assisted workflows to move faster without cutting corners.
